replies.body: hey bro i would duo if youre still interested

not trying to be eh, offensive but uh.
1 million yi mastery
silver 3
something doesn't add up.

also might as well add khazix to your jungle pool or at least play him to know what he do (hint: he bursts people 100-0 from lv3 and does this every patch)
i dont know, it feels like you are trying to play ALOT of champions. i can't help but feel if you just main <3 (thats a less than 3 not heart sign tho i do love u owo) for each roles you mentioned, (also jax can top/jg) you can climb much easier?
